<h2 id="æ§åˆ¶å‘½ä»¤">æ§åˆ¶å‘½ä»¤</h2>
<h5 id="if">@if</h5>
<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">@if</code>æŒ‡ä»¤æ˜¯ä¸€ä¸ª<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">SassScript</code>ï¼Œå®ƒå¯ä»¥æ ¹æ®æ¡ä»¶æ¥å¤„ç†æ ·å¼å—ï¼Œå¦‚æœæ¡ä»¶ä¸º<strong>true</strong>è¿”å›ä¸€ä¸ªæ ·å¼å—ï¼Œåä¹‹<strong>false</strong>è¿”å›å¦ä¸€ä¸ªæ ·å¼å—ã€‚åœ¨Sassä¸­é™¤äº†<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">@if</code>ï¼Œè¿˜å¯ä»¥é…åˆ<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">@else if</code>ã€<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">@if not</code>å’Œ<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">@else</code>ä¸€èµ·ä½¿ç”¨ã€‚
å‡è®¾è¦æ§åˆ¶ä¸€ä¸ªå…ƒç´ éšè—æˆ–æ˜¾ç¤ºï¼Œæˆ‘ä»¬å°±å¯ä»¥å®šä¹‰ä¸€ä¸ªæ··åˆå®ï¼Œé€šè¿‡<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">@if...@else...</code>æ¥åˆ¤æ–­ä¼ è¿›å‚æ•°çš„å€¼æ¥æ§åˆ¶<strong>display</strong>çš„å€¼ã€‚å¦‚ä¸‹æ‰€ç¤ºï¼š</p>
<div class="language-sass highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>    <span class="k">@mixin</span> <span class="nf">hidden</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nv">$tf</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="bp">true</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="err">{</span>
    <span class="k">@if</span> <span class="nv">$tf</span> <span class="err">{</span>
        <span class="k">@debug</span> <span class="s2">"$tf is </span><span class="si">#{</span><span class="nv">$tf</span><span class="si">}</span><span class="s2">"</span><span class="err">;</span>
        <span class="nl">display</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nb">block</span><span class="err">;</span>
        <span class="err">}</span>
    <span class="k">@else</span> <span class="err">{</span>
        <span class="k">@debug</span> <span class="s2">"$tf is </span><span class="si">#{</span><span class="nv">$tf</span><span class="si">}</span><span class="s2">"</span><span class="err">;</span>
        <span class="nl">display</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nb">none</span><span class="err">;</span>
        <span class="err">}</span>
    <span class="err">}</span>

    <span class="nc">.block</span> <span class="err">{</span>
    <span class="k">@include</span> <span class="nd">hidden</span><span class="err">;</span>
    <span class="err">}</span>

    <span class="nc">.hidden</span><span class="err">{</span>
    <span class="k">@include</span> <span class="nd">hidden</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="bp">false</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="err">;</span>
    <span class="err">}</span>

   <span class="nt">-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</span>
    <span class="c1">//ç¼–è¯‘å</span>
    <span class="nc">.block</span> <span class="err">{</span>
        <span class="nl">display</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nb">block</span><span class="err">;</span>
    <span class="err">}</span>

    <span class="nc">.hidden</span> <span class="err">{</span>
        <span class="nl">display</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nb">none</span><span class="err">;</span>
    <span class="err">}</span>   

